          <div class="scope-item"><span class="scope-x">✗</span> Noor platform integration</div>
          <div class="scope-item"><span class="scope-x">✗</span> Real-time classroom monitoring</div>
          <div class="scope-item"><span class="scope-x">✗</span> Legal IEP generation</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission -->
      <div class="mission-box">
        <div class="mission-ar">"نستثمر في 12,000 ساعة دراسية لتكون فرصاً للنمو بدلاً من الإحباط."</div>
        <div class="mission-en">"We invest in 12,000 classroom hours to become opportunities for growth rather than frustration."</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- MAIN -->
    <div class="main">

      <!-- Swarm Architecture -->
      <div>
        <div class="swarm-section">
          <div class="swarm-title">5-Agent LangGraph Swarm Architecture</div>
          <div class="swarm-sub">dynamic handoff tools · shared InMemorySaver · per-message language enforcement</div>

          <div class="swarm-flow">
            <div class="agent-node">
              <div class="agent-chip" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B4F9C,#0E3580);">🎯</div>
