            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-card">
            <div class="feat-icon" style="background:#FFF7ED;">🧠</div>
            <div class="feat-text">
              <div class="feat-title">Long-Term Memory</div>
              <div class="feat-desc">Cross-session student history injected into Orchestrator + Planning Agent prompts via Supabase.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-card">
            <div class="feat-icon" style="background:#F5F3FF;">🌐</div>
            <div class="feat-text">
              <div class="feat-title">Per-Message Language Detection</div>
              <div class="feat-desc">Arabic Unicode range check on every turn. All 5 agents get strict OUTPUT LANGUAGE rules.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-card">
            <div class="feat-icon" style="background:#FFF1F2;">🛡️</div>
            <div class="feat-text">
              <div class="feat-title">4-Layer Guardrails</div>
              <div class="feat-desc">Input validation → Agent scope → Output safety → Data access. Injected into every agent prompt.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-card">
            <div class="feat-icon" style="background:#ECFDF5;">✅</div>
            <div class="feat-text">
